node.text:
High Reps & Medium Weight! Let’s get it 🦾

I really enjoy what I do! I Make sure to keep it fun and creative! But just because I’m smiling doesn’t mean I’m not putting in work! Keep your workouts exciting and don’t overwhelm yourself with “perfection”, It will all come! SMILE a little , dance a little more & most IMPORTANTLY.. SWEAT A LOT! 🥵

I had to rock out since those were the vibes on the gym 🎸 💥 😝

SWIPE ✔️ SAVE ✔️ TRY ✔️ SHARE

This message is to inform anyone who may hate them or may just want to get rid of them! I’ve gotten great results and the best part is this treatment works for ALL skin types!

Forget what anyone tells you about what you WANT, and what you’d prefer for your BODY. It’s yours. 😘 and I SUPPORT YOU!

Thank you @simonourianmd1 💫

Under arm pits, inner thighs , Glutes , tummy etc! It can be genetic but mainly from your body changing drastically in size, losing weight gaining weight , gaining muscles , growing in size from having babies etc! Thank you @simonourianmd1 for taking care of my skin! I know stretch marks aren’t necessarily a “bad thing” but for those who may want to get rid of them or are a little timid or insecure about hiding them please contact Epion for more details! You won’t regret it! Painless treatments and more!

node.text:
This has easily become my LIFESTYLE. I’m grateful to be able to share my joy for it with you guys!

I started sports in the 7th Grade (basketball, volleyball, track) & played those sports all the way through college. Always played at a very high level , & being active was I knew! I find so much joy and excitement in competition & anything that’s going to challenge me! I may be small, but I can also be UNSTOPPABLE 🦾😈 #qimmahtherapy 

Shot by @nate_zielke_creates

node.text:
High Reps & Medium Weight! Let’s get it 🦾

I really enjoy what I do! I Make sure to keep it fun and creative! But just because I’m smiling doesn’t mean I’m not putting in work! Keep your workouts exciting and don’t overwhelm yourself with “perfection”, It will all come! SMILE a little , dance a little more & most IMPORTANTLY.. SWEAT A LOT! 🥵

I had to rock out since those were the vibes on the gym 🎸 💥 😝

SWIPE ✔️ SAVE ✔️ TRY ✔️ SHARE

node.text:
It’s a lifestyle to be Healthy Mentally for me. It has taken me such a long way. It’s been more valuable to work on my mental then my physical. But life is about balance, and it allows me to consider all aspects in my life that need work. The goal should be that Everything in your life should be “Healthy”. The mind is the only thing that can manifest that as your reality. If you don’t think it, or want it, or desire, or even believe in it, how can it be? Dream about it, pray on it, and most importantly.. LIVE IT. 💕 Every day, every step you take is one step closer. And it only gets easier.. once you recognize good, you start to feel good cause you realize THIS IS WHAT I NEED. This is what I’ve been yearning for. You’re so close, you’re right there, don’t give up. 🦾

🎥 @shotbysham
